{"tid":1507242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚，以身軀擋在槍口前的大叔，原來是一位教會傳道人","createTime":"2019-08-26T05:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T05:31:19.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da9b3c5454f14b30a954933bfdc470117c149b88","tid":1507242,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:25:38.000Z","msg":"琴晚，以身軀擋在槍口前的大叔，原來是一位教會傳道人。<br />\n<br />\n狠人以我個人觀察到基督教的牧者今次主要分為三類（基督徒朋友如有冒犯，請隨便插我）：<br />\n<br />\n1. 譴責單方或雙方暴力的人，即係見到邊個錯，就話佢地犯罪。<br />\n2. 唔出聲，事不關己的態度，以免得罪教會內的信徒<br />\n3. 願意去到前線，陪伴和保護受傷的人。仲記得喺有次示威期間，狠人喺前線見到有班牧者道為肉身，去到前線守護一班年青人，係仇恨之處播下愛。<br />\n<br />\n狠人上次係機場集會，見到有幾位基督徒（個樣似廿幾歲）好熱心，用行動關心其他示威者，又為佢地祈禱。狠人同其中一個傾過計，佢係個剛剛畢業的護士，佢話佢教會牧者次次都有去示威的現場保護班學生，呢個行為感動左好多教會裡面的人，要走出來幫手，唔係得把口。<br />\n<br />\n我聽到之後，都幾感動，有機會都想返佢教會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxtP8X8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxtP8X8.jpg&h=351aea86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/photos/a.112035443472580/122645562411568?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFinanceFellow%2Fphotos%2Fa.112035443472580%2F122645562411568%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=ebdd7706\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/photos/a.112035443472580/122645562411568?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ff0e1a11279ef507c2c93360dd57993cb26b4740","tid":1507242,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:28:54.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣一下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4GJMrJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4GJMrJb.jpg&h=cb7c9807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n901 和你塞  13:00 見   <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=TNp%2FFCzVUvAW3I%2FC9AhTYwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=fc7e314e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"4ec8b36ceb9f6dfea905ff365f50294016c5461d","tid":1507242,"uid":77532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:29:00.000Z","msg":"重覆咗<br />\n唔推"},{"pid":"cc7311297cf72634a1dc1d7f2fbfabfecb4d019a","tid":1507242,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"屋企人係教會裡面唔講，但離開教會就時時刻刻講政治，又會發夢。私下知有教友係示威者，都會有獨立Group傾。<br />\n<br />\n但就唔想影響教會運作，其實同一般人唔想係家庭Group講政治差唔多。"}]}